race.comment: YES I KNOW (10) is fitter for two runs back and looks cherry ripe now. Good fresh and even better second-up with a close-up third over the mile. Extra trip is ideal now and expected to go close. FIORENOT (8) is going along well in marginally easier races, the latest a close-up third over this journey at Caulfield Heath. Placed 3/3 this time in and looks due to break through. Gets his chance off the low draw. DRAW ATTENTION (16) is an emerging galloper fitter for two runs back. Both runs have been excellent finishing close to the winner and ideally placed up in journey now. Is a third-up winner and should run well. BLUE COWBOY (11) is in great form winning two of four this time in, scoring the latest over a similar trip at Geelong. Drops in weight on that and will take catching. THORIN (4)  is another who put the writing on the wall second-up with a narrow placing and now looks ready to hit his straps.
